<title>CHINA: Shanghai Forever bonus issue approved.</title>
<headline>Shanghai Forever bonus issue approved.</headline>
<dateline>SHANGHAI 1997-06-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shareholders of Shanghai Forever Co Ltd have approved a 1.5-for-10 bonus share issue, the company said on Saturday in a statement in the Shanghai Securities News.</p>
<p>Bicycle maker Shanghai Forever posted a 37.47 million yuan loss for 1996 based on international accounting standards, compared with a loss of 19.66 million yuan in 1995.</p>
<p>($1 = 8.3 yuan)</p>
<p>-- Shanghai newsroom (86-21) 6279-7004</p>
